97ASN1_OBJECT *OBJ_dup(const ASN1_OBJECT *o) {
98 ASN1_OBJECT *r;
99 unsigned char *data = NULL;
100 char *sn = NULL, *ln = NULL;
101
102 if (o == NULL) {
103 return NULL;
104 }
105
106 if (!(o->flags & ASN1_OBJECT_FLAG_DYNAMIC)) {
107 // TODO(fork): this is a little dangerous.
108 return (ASN1_OBJECT *)o;
109 }
110
111 r = ASN1_OBJECT_new();
112 if (r == NULL) {
113 OPENSSL_PUT_ERROR(OBJ, ERR_R_ASN1_LIB);
114 return NULL;
115 }
116 r->ln = r->sn = NULL;
117
118 data = OPENSSL_malloc(o->length);
119 if (data == NULL) {
120 goto err;
121 }
122 if (o->data != NULL) {
123 OPENSSL_memcpy(data, o->data, o->length);
124 }
125
126 // once data is attached to an object, it remains const
127 r->data = data;
128 r->length = o->length;
129 r->nid = o->nid;
130
131 if (o->ln != NULL) {
132 ln = OPENSSL_strdup(o->ln);
133 if (ln == NULL) {
134 goto err;
135 }
136 }
137
138 if (o->sn != NULL) {
139 sn = OPENSSL_strdup(o->sn);
140 if (sn == NULL) {
141 goto err;
142 }
143 }
144
145 r->sn = sn;
146 r->ln = ln;
147
148 r->flags =
149 o->flags | (ASN1_OBJECT_FLAG_DYNAMIC | ASN1_OBJECT_FLAG_DYNAMIC_STRINGS |
150 ASN1_OBJECT_FLAG_DYNAMIC_DATA);
151 return r;
152
153err:
154 OPENSSL_PUT_ERROR(OBJ, ERR_R_MALLOC_FAILURE);
155 OPENSSL_free(ln);
156 OPENSSL_free(sn);
157 OPENSSL_free(data);
158 OPENSSL_free(r);
159 return NULL;
160}

204int OBJ_obj2nid(const ASN1_OBJECT *obj) {
205 if (obj == NULL) {
206 return NID_undef;
207 }
208
209 if (obj->nid != 0) {
210 return obj->nid;
211 }
212
213 CRYPTO_STATIC_MUTEX_lock_read(&global_added_lock);
214 if (global_added_by_data != NULL) {
215 ASN1_OBJECT *match;
216
217 match = lh_ASN1_OBJECT_retrieve(global_added_by_data, obj);
218 if (match != NULL) {
219 CRYPTO_STATIC_MUTEX_unlock_read(&global_added_lock);
220 return match->nid;
221 }
222 }
223 CRYPTO_STATIC_MUTEX_unlock_read(&global_added_lock);
224
225 const uint16_t *nid_ptr =
226 bsearch(obj, kNIDsInOIDOrder, OPENSSL_ARRAY_SIZE(kNIDsInOIDOrder),
227 sizeof(kNIDsInOIDOrder[0]), obj_cmp);
228 if (nid_ptr == NULL) {
229 return NID_undef;
230 }
231
232 return kObjects[*nid_ptr].nid;
233}

432 // Python depends on the empty OID successfully encoding as the empty
433 // string.
434 if (obj == NULL || obj->length == 0) {

439 int nid = OBJ_obj2nid(obj);

442 if (name == NULL) {
443 name = OBJ_nid2sn(nid);

445 if (name != NULL) {

454 if (txt == NULL) {
455 if (out_len > 0) {
456 out[0] = '\0';
457 }
458 return -1;
459 }
460
461 int ret = strlcpy_int(out, txt, out_len);
462 OPENSSL_free(txt);
463 return ret;

502// obj_add_object inserts |obj| into the various global hashes for run-time
503// added objects. It returns one on success or zero otherwise.
504static int obj_add_object(ASN1_OBJECT *obj) {
505 int ok;
506 ASN1_OBJECT *old_object;
507
508 obj->flags &= ~(ASN1_OBJECT_FLAG_DYNAMIC | ASN1_OBJECT_FLAG_DYNAMIC_STRINGS |
509 ASN1_OBJECT_FLAG_DYNAMIC_DATA);
510
511 CRYPTO_STATIC_MUTEX_lock_write(&global_added_lock);
512 if (global_added_by_nid == NULL) {
513 global_added_by_nid = lh_ASN1_OBJECT_new(hash_nid, cmp_nid);
514 global_added_by_data = lh_ASN1_OBJECT_new(hash_data, cmp_data);
515 global_added_by_short_name = lh_ASN1_OBJECT_new(hash_short_name, cmp_short_name);
516 global_added_by_long_name = lh_ASN1_OBJECT_new(hash_long_name, cmp_long_name);
517 }
518
519 // We don't pay attention to |old_object| (which contains any previous object
520 // that was evicted from the hashes) because we don't have a reference count
521 // on ASN1_OBJECT values. Also, we should never have duplicates nids and so
522 // should always have objects in |global_added_by_nid|.
523
524 ok = lh_ASN1_OBJECT_insert(global_added_by_nid, &old_object, obj);
525 if (obj->length != 0 && obj->data != NULL) {
526 ok &= lh_ASN1_OBJECT_insert(global_added_by_data, &old_object, obj);
527 }
528 if (obj->sn != NULL) {
529 ok &= lh_ASN1_OBJECT_insert(global_added_by_short_name, &old_object, obj);
530 }
531 if (obj->ln != NULL) {
532 ok &= lh_ASN1_OBJECT_insert(global_added_by_long_name, &old_object, obj);
533 }
534 CRYPTO_STATIC_MUTEX_unlock_write(&global_added_lock);
535
536 return ok;
537}
